Subject: LA witnesses 
Hi all, 
MI and I are heading to Los Angeles in late August to prep with a number of trial witnesses in the Maxwell case. In 
advance of the trip, I'm going to begin drafting q&as, and it would be super helpful to have a binder with some 
information about two of the witnesses. When you can, could someone please put together a binder with all witness 
interview notes and 302s for the following two witnesses? Thanks so much. No labels on the binders needed — just tabs 
with dates of interviews would be great (e.g., M., 7-6-19 interview). 
• 
• 
These materials should be in their 3500 folders. 
Thanks! 
Assistant United States Attorney 
Southern District of New York 
EFTA00032476
